    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}What's wrong? Not hungry?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="SEL_004_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}That's not it.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Why'd you bring me here?]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}...Alright, then.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}Well, you're still growing. You can handle at least one bowl of ramen.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}'Cause I said I'd treat you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}I can't go back on my word. It's bad for my conscience.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="SEL_007_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}That makes sense.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}You're so faithful.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I forgot about that.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}I'm just keeping the promises I made, that's all...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 6 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 6 25 25}...That supposed to be a compliment?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 1 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}Heh, sure you did.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}Here ya go, two specials![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}Point is, you don't go back on your word. 'Specially when it comes to somethin' you promised.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="SEL_013_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}This looks delicious.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Let's eat.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}...Right, don't want the noodles to get soggy.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}I was thinkin', earlier... you really don't take any shit, even from your elders.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}I respect straightforwardness. Less trouble that way.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}Let's finish up and get the hell outta here.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
